{"tid":1386824,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"捐「coupon」 與 捐「裝備」 利弊分析","createTime":"2019-07-30T12:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:28:22.000Z","uid":14409,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"060fcfb53378454919ac130cd6cea947b4be6d0d","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:01:46.000Z","msg":"站喺細路仔角度而言，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 細路仔心態</span></span><br />\n雖然我甚少接觸佢哋，<span style=\"color: red;\">但睇咗好多文話佢哋連人哋請食飯都覺得唔好意思，更何況要佢哋主動去拎呢啲禮券？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n如果係裝備嘅話，就好似一般人去物資站拎野，各取所需又唔會尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 金額大細</span></span><br />\n一副全裝至少$500以上。<br />\n一餐飯幾十至$100不等。<br />\n自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">3. 實用</span>性</span><br />\n如果細路仔有心做前線，裝備實用性絕對係100%。<br />\nCoupon相對較弱，食肆禮券會比較可取，惠康百佳嗰啲就。。。。不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">4.<span style=\"font-size: large;\">可行性</span></span><br />\n我硬係覺得如果就咁派禮券，一定會有啲閒人走嚟拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗大部份人點解會捐禮卷嘅原因係佢哋根本唔知道喺邊度買裝，但如果有人可以集齊晒啲錢去專買裝備呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會捐裝 ： 正評<br />\n我會捐禮卷 : 負評"},{"pid":"62fd04ce77f869801d6e870aebb169d592aea3ea","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:02:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8d7183e8915e9031fe72601324b18b370de9fd","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:03:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc5aa88f508341a7516d579c0c75f8efd2ee654","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28fb2bbd46c9690def5fac9a270bfbffb4659ca","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:05:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c063694b0adeb1401daa020a203c044ce1d774","tid":1386824,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:06:47.000Z","msg":"借個位 唔該大家幫手傳開去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係眾籌出書今日係旺角東天橋擺街站的手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1386480/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1386480/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望係旺角附近的手足提提係我地原來擺街站的位置(近moko) 的有心人 今日因警方關係唔再擺 請早d回家休息 我地後日會繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地的義工已經安全撤離, 現埸有消息指有&quot;義工&quot;收集近現金券,<br />\n戴定個頭盔, 小心任何我地撤離後的&quot;義工&quot;, 我地無辦法控制佢地收集左之後會點用 <br />\n<br />\n另外 造成混亂 真係好唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期四再見"},{"pid":"ed99a344994c67b3e9850479d804b41728cb599d","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:13:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca216fd31026bca94b8acbbdfc2194dee13b3b55","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"直接課金買裝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89d6ce6ffd16faa0ba552572105d71159419f3b","tid":1386824,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"大家覺得我應該買五套全 set 定 10套濾罐？全送出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGds4ai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGds4ai.png&h=b7aec32f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"097fc3123b1dfc02b08a19317bf28812fcc99769","tid":1386824,"uid":14409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d89d6ce6ffd16faa0ba552572105d71159419f3b","tid":1386824,"uid":18948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"大家覺得我應該買五套全 set 定 10套濾罐？全送出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MGds4ai.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMGds4ai.png&h=b7aec32f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T12:28:22.000Z","msg":"乜都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以開個group專門幫佢地一把"}]}